  "title": "Is cutaneous tuberculosis infectious? A case presentation and practical management plan.",
  "abstract": "Infection control measures for cutaneous tuberculosis in the absence of pulmonary disease are problematic. Delays in diagnosis can lead to the exposure of many individuals. This article describes a case of cutaneous tuberculosis and the subsequent contact investigation. Strategies for infection control and their practicality are discussed.",
